<apex:page
  showHeader="false"
  sidebar="false"
  standardStylesheets="false"
  applyHtmlTag="false"
  applyBodyTag="false"
  renderAs="pdf"
>
  <html>
    <head>
      <meta charset="UTF-8" />
      <title>Company Report</title>
      <style>
        body {
          font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
          font-size: 14px;
        }
        .header {
          text-align: left;
          border-bottom: 2px solid #000;
          padding-bottom: 10px;
          margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .header img {
          width: 100px;
          vertical-align: middle;
        }
        .header .title {
          display: inline-block;
          text-align: center;
          margin-left: 10px;
        }
        .header h1,
        .header h2,
        .header h3 {
          margin: 0;
        }
        .header h1 {
          color: #00aaff;
          font-size: 18px;
        }
        .form-section h2 {
          color: #00aaff;
          font-size: 14px;
          text-align: center;
        }
        .form-section {
          border: 1px solid #000;
          padding: 10px;
          margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .form-group {
          margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .form-group-left {
          align-content: left;
        }
        .form-group-right {
          text-align: right;
        }

        .form-group h4 {
          display: inline-block;
          width: 100px;
          font-weight: bold;
          margin: 0;
        }
        .form-group input {
          width: 200px;
        }
        .inline-group {
          display: flex;
          justify-content: space-between;
        }
        .questions {
          margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .questions p {
          font-weight: bold;
        }
        .question {
          margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .question h2,
        .question h3 {
          margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .question .choice {
          display: block;
          margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        .check {
          width: 10px;
          height: 10px;
          vertical-align: middle;
        }
        .center-align {
          text-align: center;
        }
      </style>
    </head>
    <body>
      <div class="header">
        <img src="{!URLFOR($Resource.Logo)}" alt="DesClick Formation" />
      </div>

      <div class="form-section">
        <div class="title">
          <h2>
            Formation Hygiène et Sécurité alimentaire en restauration
            Commerciale
          </h2>
          <h2>Quiz 5</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="form-group-left">
          <h4>Nom :</h4>
        </div>

        <div class="form-group">
          <h4>Date :</h4>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="questions">
        <p>Veuillez cocher la bonne réponse.</p>

        <div class="question">
          <h3>
            1. Quelles sont les conséquences d’une rupture de chaine de froid ?
          </h3>
          <table>
            <tbody>
              <tr>
                <td class="center-align">
                  <img
                    src="{!URLFOR($Resource.uncheckbox)}"
                    alt=""
                    class="check"
                  />
                </td>
                <td>Raccourcie la DLC</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td class="center-align">
                  <img
                    src="{!URLFOR($Resource.uncheckbox)}"
                    alt=""
                    class="check"
                  />
                </td>
                <td>Périme les aliments</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td class="center-align">
                  <img
                    src="{!URLFOR($Resource.uncheckbox)}"
                    alt=""
                    class="check"
                  />
                </td>
                <td>Intoxication alimentaire</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td class="center-align">
                  <img
                    src="{!URLFOR($Resource.uncheckbox)}"
                    alt=""
                    class="check"
                  />
                </td>
                <td>Provoque la prolifération des bactéries</td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>

        <div class="question">
          <h3>2. La décongélation peut être faite à température ambiante?</h3>
          <table>
            <tbody>
              <tr>
                <td class="center-align">
                  <img
                    src="{!URLFOR($Resource.uncheckbox)}"
                    alt=""
                    class="check"
                  />
                </td>
                <td>Vrai</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td class="center-align">
                  <img
                    src="{!URLFOR($Resource.uncheckbox)}"
                    alt=""
                    class="check"
                  />
                </td>
                <td>Faux</td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>

        <div class="question">
          <h3>3. A quelle température doit-on conserver le poisson ?</h3>
          <table>
            <tbody>
              <tr>
                <td class="center-align">
                  <img
                    src="{!URLFOR($Resource.uncheckbox)}"
                    alt=""
                    class="check"
                  />
                </td>
                <td>0°C à 2°C</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td class="center-align">
                  <img
                    src="{!URLFOR($Resource.uncheckbox)}"
                    alt=""
                    class="check"
                  />
                </td>
                <td>2°C à 4°C</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td class="center-align">
                  <img
                    src="{!URLFOR($Resource.uncheckbox)}"
                    alt=""
                    class="check"
                  />
                </td>
                <td>4°C à 6°C</td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>

        <div class="question">
          <h3>4. Assurer la rotation c’est</h3>
          <table>
            <tbody>
              <tr>
                <td class="center-align">
                  <img
                    src="{!URLFOR($Resource.uncheckbox)}"
                    alt=""
                    class="check"
                  />
                </td>
                <td>Respecter les règles de rangement par date</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td class="center-align">
                  <img
                    src="{!URLFOR($Resource.uncheckbox)}"
                    alt=""
                    class="check"
                  />
                </td>
                <td>Utiliser un produit DLC est dépassé</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td class="center-align">
                  <img
                    src="{!URLFOR($Resource.uncheckbox)}"
                    alt=""
                    class="check"
                  />
                </td>
                <td>Changer la date quand je change de film</td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
      </div>

      <section>
        <br /><br />
        <br />
        <br /><br />
        <br />
        <div style="float: left; width: 50%; text-align: center">
          <p></p>
        </div>
        <div style="float: right; width: 50%; text-align: center">
          <p>
            <strong> Nom Stagaire </strong>
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>
    </body>
  </html>
</apex:page>
